room_title: Escape room "MacGregor Manor" by Game On Escapes & More in Raleigh - Durham
room_description:
Congratulations on the purchase of your new home! Your friends can't believe you bought it sight unseen, let alone the fact that no one has seen the inside of MacGregor Manor since 1974. The last known viewers passed away in a car accident shortly after recording some footage from within.
Some believe it to be cursed, because of all of the misfortunes that befall those that enter. You have 60 minutes to change break the curse or change your mind before the lawyer files for the paperwork in the courthouse.
